#new:String $GoombariusQuip
{
[Style Right]
Is...[Pause 5] Is it finally over?[BR]
[Pause 5]I can rest.[Pause 3] No more crazy demons[BR]
trying to kill me or nothing?[BR]
[Wait][Next]
[PrintGrowing]Thank God...[/fx][BR]
[Pause 10]Old Goombarius was gonna age way[BR]
too rapidly if that kept happening.[BR]
[Pause 4]I need to stay young, dang it![BR]
[Wait][End]
}

#new:String $KooperQuip
{
[Style Tattle]
[PrintGrowing]Pant...[/fx][Pause 5] did...[Pause 5] did we do it?[BR]
[Wait][End]
}

#new:String $BombetteQuip
{
[Style Tattle]
We beat it.[BR]
[Pause 8]It's all over...[BR]
[Wait][End]
}

#new:String $ParakariusQuip
{
[Style Tattle]
[Shake]I was makin' brownies in my[BR]
pants the whole time.[BR]
That was scary, bro.[BR]
[Wait][End]
}

#new:String $BowQuip
{
[Style Tattle]
Hmph. Hardly a challenge for me[BR]
and my servant.[BR]
[Wait][End]
}

#new:String $WattageQuip
{
[Style Tattle]
[PrintRising]Yippee. We beat it.[BR]
We really beat it![/fx][BR]
[Wait][End]
}

#new:String $SushieQuip
{
[Style Tattle]
It was a rough time, but we[BR]
managed to pull through,[BR]
didn't we?[BR]
[Wait][End]
}

#new:String $JonathanQuip
{
[Style Tattle]
Yeah, dude![Pause 5][PrintRising] In yo face![/fx][BR]
[Pause 5]We rocked that devil![BR]
[Wait][End]
}

#new:String $Shisho1
{
[Style Tattle]
Ah... there you are.[BR]
[Wait][End]
}

#new:String $Shisho2
{
[Style Right]
Mario-san,[Pause 5] I surmise you must be[BR]
shocked to see me here.[BR]
[Pause 12]Is that not correct?[BR]
[Wait][End]
}

#new:String $PartnerQuip
{
[Style Tattle]
Shisho? What are you doing here?[BR]
[Wait][End]
}

#new:String $Chan1
{
[Style Right]
O Wise One,[Pause 4] our great master[BR]
detected a disturbance from[BR]
beyond [SaveColor][Color:1D]Goomba Village[RestoreColor][Pause 3] the moment[BR]
the last [SaveColor][Color:09]Love Deity[RestoreColor] was rescued.[BR]
[Wait][Next]
His senses were right.[BR]
[Pause 5]You were battling a great evil all[BR]
by your lonesome?[BR]
[Wait][End]
}

#new:String $Lee1
{
[Style Right]
Honestly, we were quite worried he[BR]
wasn't going to make it.[BR]
[Pause 10]The glare of evil from this crypt[BR]
was making his chest ache.[BR]
[Wait][Next]
Shisho's heartrate was skyrocketing.[BR]
[Pause 5]He was in immense pain, so we had[BR]
to escort him all the way here.[BR]
[Wait][End]
}

#new:String $Shisho3
{
[Style Right]
Yes,[Pause 5] my disciples know me too well.[BR]
[Pause 12]I, of course, knew of the demons[BR]
that dwelled beneath this land.[BR]
[Wait][Next]
My ancestor was very fond of[BR]
Masuta-san and his research.[BR]
[Pause 10]To think,[Pause 5] the [SaveColor][Color:09]Love Deities[RestoreColor] were the[BR]
ones binding the seal...[BR]
[Wait][End]
}

#new:String $Shisho4
{
[Style Right]
Allow me to get to the point.[BR]
[Pause 15]The man you see before you.[BR]
[Pause 5]His name is not [SaveColor][Color:09]Pries T.[RestoreColor][BR]
[Wait][Next]
When [SaveColor][Color:04]Xin Suì[RestoreColor] corrupted him. He lost[BR]
his memories on who he was and the [BR]
daemon made him adopt the moniker[BR]of [SaveColor][Color:09]Pries T.[RestoreColor]
[Wait][End]
}

#new:String $Chan2
{
[Style Right]
Sensei,[Pause 5] you said you would get[BR]
straight to the point.[BR]
[Wait][End]
}

#new:String $Lee2
{
[Style Right]
You're withholding the most crucial[BR]
piece of information, Sensei.[BR]
[Wait][End]
}

#new:String $Shisho5
{
[Style Right]
Am I?[Pause 15] ....[PrintRising].Of course![/fx][BR]
[Pause 10][Shake]Cough... hack... ack...[/fx][BR]
[Wait][Next]
Mario-san...[Pause 5] the man you've been[BR]
fighting to save all this time...[BR]
[Wait][End]
}

#new:String $Shisho6
{
[Style Right]
[Pause 10][Speed delay=2 chars=1]He is my grandson,[Pause 15] [SaveColor][Color:09]Prince Mush[RestoreColor].[BR]
[Wait][End]
}

#new:String $Shisho7
{
[Style Right]
Mario-san...[Pause 10] thank you for returning[BR]
my grandson to me.[BR]
[Pause 10]I am most grateful to you.[BR]
[Wait][End]
}

#new:String $Chan3
{
[Style Right]
To see our Sensei so happy...[BR]
[Pause 8]it makes me happy too.[BR]
[Wait][End]
}

#new:String $Lee3
{
[Style Right]
Such a touching reunion.[BR]
It brings tears to my eyes.[BR]
[Wait][End]
}

#new:String $Mush
{
[Style  Tattle]
Ugh.... where... am I?[BR]
[Wait][End]
}

#new:String $Shisho8
{
[Style Right]
You need not speak,[Pause 2] my grandson.[BR]
[Pause 8]The way of the [SaveColor][Color:05]Saiyan[RestoreColor] is calling.[BR]
[Pause 6]Once you rest your body and mind,[BR]
we can resume your training.[BR]
[Wait][Next]
For now,[Pause 2] we need to get you back[BR]
to [SaveColor][Color:05]Kino House[RestoreColor].[BR]
[Pause 5]The island awaits your triumphant[BR]
return, Mush-san.[BR]
[Wait][End]
}

#new:String $Shisho9
{
[Style Right]
As always, Mario-san,[Pause 2] you're free[BR]
to come spar with me and my students[BR]
during any off-time you have.[BR]
[Wait][Next]
[Pause 20]Hmmm? [Pause 10]You say you need to be[BR]
heading to [SaveColor][Color:09]Love Heaven[RestoreColor] now?[BR]
[Pause 12]Ah, that takes me back...[BR]
[Wait][Next]
It must be an incredibly important[BR]
venture for you then.[BR]
